OL,3,C'From the sublime to the ridiculous':
OL,4,CFarmer's crop concerns amid June
OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FA farmer's daughter in Bromsgrove in
OL,8,FWorcestershire says they're facing
OL,9,F"real anxiety" for their winter crops
OL,10,Fduring the current heatwave.
OL,12,FBethan Window says the lack of rain
OL,13,Fhas severely impacted the growth of
OL,14,Fhay which means they might struggle to
OL,15,Fhave animal feed over the winter
OL,16,Fchanges.
