OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,F"You don't know what hand you're going
OL,8,Fto be dealt, it can go from the
OL,9,Fsublime to the ridiculous, there's no
OL,10,Fin between."
OL,12,FNot only is it worrying for animals,
OL,13,Fbut there are health warnings for
OL,14,Fhumans too.
OL,16,FOne pharmacist says people need to
OL,17,Fprotect themselves as best they can
OL,18,Fduring this heatwave.
OL,20,FPavan Shocker, a community pharmacist
OL,21,Fin Telford suggests:
