OL,5,Cheatwave
OL,7,FHe said, "If people on insulin, they
OL,8,Fshould keep a cooler with them, like a
OL,9,Fcooling pack.
OL,11,F"Storage-wise on the medication will
OL,12,Fsay 30 degrees roughly for the
OL,13,Ftemperature maximum, anything above
OL,14,Fthat the potency will decrease.
OL,16,F"So make sure you put it in a cool,
OL,17,Fdry place away from the sun."
